{"tid":1627633,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"九月初九，勇武和理非休息一日，將個波拋番比政府，贏藍屍民心","createTime":"2019-10-05T16:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:39:20.000Z","uid":164907,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"698672bd6a262c23b8a267ebd9efd6a7f4a73bfb","tid":1627633,"uid":164907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"九月初九，重陽，全世界休息一日。<br />\n只做好事，扶阿波過馬路，文宣工作<br />\n<br />\n自推10連<br />\n<br />\n贏藍屍民心，贏國際層面，將個波拋番比政府假戒嚴"},{"pid":"3ddddf51a317b8b769f165bb8222a5d9db4f8502","tid":1627633,"uid":164907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:53:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67c53b392e9e464b5718cbb2f0029b7287a7992f","tid":1627633,"uid":9521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:54:05.000Z","msg":"和唔和理非係睇班狗<br />\n唔係由市民決定<br />\n可以和理非但都一定要帶gear"},{"pid":"1e43c9b064cbb61441505cee550b2327956bd5d1","tid":1627633,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:55:38.000Z","msg":"暫時休息下 做下文宣 敵進我退崖過區選"},{"pid":"4b8a59d00b438a39797729c85c353d7fd4aadb39","tid":1627633,"uid":164907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c53b392e9e464b5718cbb2f0029b7287a7992f","tid":1627633,"uid":9521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:54:05.000Z","msg":"和唔和理非係睇班狗<br />\n唔係由市民決定<br />\n可以和理非但都一定要帶gear"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:57:42.000Z","msg":"10月7，星期一，九月初九，邊個先做野就輸撚緊<br />\n<br />\n政府10月7號重開黨鐵，你個日攪尻佢=燒藍屍山墳<br />\n<br />\n內到外都輸撚硬<br />\n<br />\n倒不如路做野休息一日，贏藍屍民意"},{"pid":"08fd957cafcc39a9e3a0ace819dfb0e5fc099069","tid":1627633,"uid":164907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:59:31.000Z","msg":"星期一一定要全世界和平，忍24個鐘<br />\n唔可以有任何人多聚集堵路<br />\n和理非文宣<br />\n勇武扶阿婆過馬路，交通指揮<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳"},{"pid":"0a002522e2b694921f44e094900e72bf1a2d7493","tid":1627633,"uid":164907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:00:19.000Z","msg":"聽日朝早我會再